            "title": "超微正式向輝達宣戰！Helios全面量產第三季末出貨 OpenAI年底大規模部署",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\" data-component=\"blocks\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"超微正式向輝達宣戰！Helios全面量產第三季末出貨 OpenAI年底大規模部署\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"541\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/0ab72c206be2ceb7708025a09bce4913def9c069945242e787d9e290fae30e0c/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fcnyes_hk_559%2F0de7ade9e311a1ddf740b1a3c774f145\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">超微正式向輝達宣戰！Helios全面量產第三季末出貨 OpenAI年底大規模部署</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
