        {
            "title": "Alphabet百年債首次跌破面值九成 超大規模雲服務商債券信用利差走闊",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\" data-component=\"blocks\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"665\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/cd72d8568a03e859f358f10649935d93d98a495f1a3c96073b0c850d9a814672/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fbloomberg_chinese_traditional_757%2Fbb61042bc80f660d82ffbf05a653449b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】-- Alphabet Inc.今年早些時候在全球大舉發債之際，於英鎊市場發行了一只100年期債券，這只債券價格首次跌破了每英鎊面值買價90便士。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博匯編的數據顯示，這只10億英鎊（13.4億美元）、2126年到期的債券周四報89.978便士。這家科技巨頭今年2月發行這只債券時，發行價略低於面值。其相對於無風險基準利率的風險溢價一度觸及139.8個基點的高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在全球所有達到基準規模的高級公司債中，這只債券的剩餘期限最長。它正同時受到兩方面衝擊，一是市場擔憂與人工智能相關的債券發行，二是在財政赤字和通膨憂慮再起之際，政府債券殖利率普遍上升。由於其修正久期很長，殖利率每上升1個百分點，這只債券的價格可能下跌近15便士。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1ac8b498-c896-3bc2-833b-bd0031c9d320-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"665\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/bae16aad031558ce41a6c05841d0191bcf6e5796562143a379cbf62fc210d2b0/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fbloomberg_chinese_traditional_757%2F21c693e0145b7ecd263aa254a81ebebc\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，裕信銀行信貸策略師Michael Teig周四在一份報告中寫道：「超大規模雲服務商債券的信用利差近期擴大，再次引發投資者對其商業模式可行性的辯論，尤其是在這些公司資本支出規模龐大的背景下。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博匯編的數據，Alphabet及另一家超大規模雲服務商亞馬遜的長期債券周四在歐元投資級債券市場中跌幅居前。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Alphabet's Century Bond Has Now Lost a 10th of Its Face Value</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":\"0\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
